com.googlecode.rockit.javaAPI.formulas.expressions.impl

Class PredicateExpression

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.rockit.javaAPI.formulas.expressions.impl.PredicateExpression
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IfExpression

    public class PredicateExpression
extends Object
implements IfExpression
    Contains the predicate and a list of variables for instantiating the predicate. The list of variables must be as long as the Type List for the predicate. Further, the variables must have the same types than the predicates.
    Author:
    jan
